3C/span>  \u003Cspan class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/SD56763J\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/SD56763J\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Quint · Antoni · Aqu\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Quint\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Quint\">Q\u003C/span>\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Antoni\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Antoni\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">A͡N͡T\u003C/span>O\u003C/span>\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aqu\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Aqu\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">A͡Q\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Manganaro 1999: [(?)τ]ο͂ · ναο͂ · Ἀθ[αναίας(?)]\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Quintus Antonius Aqu(---)\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Originally and incorrectly reported by Manganaro as a brick fragment and read as a text in Greek and attributed to the Museo Archeologico Regionale di Siracusa \"Paolo Orsi\". The case of the names is unknown, nominative or genitive most likely. The final element is a cognomen, such as Aquila, Aquilinus or Aquinus (see Walthall and Korhonen for full discussion).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 49.1317.3 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1999 47 no.37 fig.112 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Walthall, Korhonen 2024 309-311 \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Neatly incised letters of slightly varying height and use of ligatures with short vertical interpuncts. Slight curvature to the strokes and tails rather than serifs.\u003C/p> Line 1  21-28  Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[204,207,210,213,216,219,222,225],{"id":205,"html":206},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: \u003Ca href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/SD56763J\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/SD56763J\u003C/a>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"la\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Quint · Antoni · Aqu\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\"